{"kanda":6,"sarga":62,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"स तुराक्षसशार्दूलोनिद्रामदसमाकुलः ।राजमार्गंश्रियाजुष्टंययौविपुलविक्रमः","trans":"He (Kumbhakaran), who was endowed with indomitable prowess, a tiger among Rakshasas, was sleepy and inebriated, marched along the splendid royal path.","words":[{"d":"विपुलविक्रमः","m":"of indomitable prowess"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"राक्षसशार्दूलः","m":"tiger among Rakshasas"},{"d":"निद्रामदसमाकुलः","m":"sleepy and inebriated"},{"d":"श्रिया","m":"prosperous"},{"d":"जुष्टम्","m":"splendid"},{"d":"राजमार्गम्","m":"royal path"},{"d":"ययौ","m":"marched."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"राक्षसानांसहस्रैश्चवृतःपरमदुर्जयः ।गृहेभ्यःपुष्पवर्षेणकीर्यमाणस्तदाययौ","trans":"Then, Kumbhakarna, who is very difficult to win over, walked violently surrounded by Rakshasas, covered with showers of flowers from houses.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"परमदुर्जयः","m":"very difficult to win"},{"d":"राक्षसानाम्","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"सहस्रैः","m":"violently"},{"d":"वृतः","m":"surrounded"},{"d":"गृहेभ्यः","m":"from the houses"},{"d":"पुष्पवर्षेण","m":"rain of flowers"},{"d":"कीर्यमाणः","m":"covered"},{"d":"ययौ","m":"went."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"स हेमजालविततंभानुभास्वरदर्शनम् ।ददर्शविपुलंरम्यंराक्षसेन्द्रनिवेशनम्","trans":"He saw the vast abode of the king of Rakshasas, with lattice work of gold and looking bright like the morning Sun","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"हेमजालविततम्","m":"latticework of gold"},{"d":"भानुभास्वरदर्शनम्","m":"bright as morning Sun"},{"d":"विपुलम्","m":"vast"},{"d":"रम्यम्","m":"delightful"},{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्रनिवेशनम्","m":"Rakshasa king's abode"},{"d":"ददर्श","m":"saw."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"स तत्तदासूर्यइवाभ्रजालंप्रविश्यरक्षोधिपतेर्निवेशम् ।ददर्शदूरेऽग्रजमासनस्थंस्वयम्भुवंशक्रवासनस्थम्","trans":"He saw entering the abode of Lord of Rakshasas like the Sun penetrating into a mass of clouds, from a distance his elder brother seated on the throne just like Indra saw the SelfBorn Brahma on the throne.","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"