विबोधितः शंसकस्माद्भयंतेऽत्रकोऽद्यप्रेतोभविष्यति ।","trans":"\"O King! For what purpose have I been awakened by you? Whom are you fearing? I wish to know who is to be ceased in life?\"","words":[{"d":"राजन्","m":"king"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"अदृत्य","m":"awakened"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"by you"},{"d":"किमर्थम्","m":"for what purpose"},{"d":"विबोधितः","m":"tell me"},{"d":"अद्य","m":"you may"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"कस्मात्","m":"with the task"},{"d":"भयम्","m":"fear"},{"d":"शंस","m":"doubt"},{"d":"प्रेतः","m":"to be ceased"},{"d":"भविष्यति","m":"I wish to know."}]},{"v":12,"dev":"भ्रातरंरावणःक्रुद्धंकुम्भकर्णमवस्थितम् ईषत्तुपरिवृत्ताभ्यांनेत्राभ्यांवाक्यमब्रवीत् ।","trans":"Kumbhakarna, was overcome with anger, and asked his brother Ravana, who was seated and rolling his eyes in anger.","words":[{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"क्रुद्धम्","m":"angry"},{"d":"अवस्थितम्","m":"seated"},{"d":"भ्रातरम्","m":"brother"},{"d":"कुम्भकर्णम्","m":"Kumbhakarna"},{"d":"ईषत्तु","m":"overcome with anger"},{"d":"परिवृत्ताभ्याम्","m":"rolling"},{"d":"नेत्राभ्याम्","m":"eyes"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"said."}]},{"v":13,"dev":"अद्यतेसुमहान्कालश्शयानस्यमहाबल सुखितस्त्वं न जानीषेममरामकृतंभयम् ।","trans":"\"Oh! Kumbhakarna of extraordinary prowess! You were asleep for long happily. You do not know that I am afraid of Rama.\"","words":[{"d":"महाबल","m":"extraordinary prowess"},{"d":"शयानस्य","m":"from sleep"},{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"अद्य","m":"arouse"},{"d":"सुमहान्","m":"long"},{"d":"कालः","m":"time"},{"d":"सुखितः","m":"sleeping"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"मम","m":"me"},{"d":"रामकृतम्","m":"of Rama"},{"d":"भयम्","m":"fear"},{"d":"न जानीषे","m":"not know."}]},{"v":14,"dev":"एषदाशरथीरामःसुग्रीवसहितोबली समुद्रंसबलस्तीर्त्वामूलंनःपरिकृन्तति ।","trans":"\"Rama, the son of Dasaratha accompanied by Sugriva, crossed the ocean with an army that was cutting our roots.\"","words":[{"d":"दाशरथिः","m":"Dasarathi"},{"d":"बली","m":"strong"},{"d":"एषः","m":"he"},{"d"