lled"},{"d":"युद्धे","m":"in combat"},{"d":"वानराणाम्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"क्षयम्","m":"killed"},{"d":"कदाचन","m":"but even"},{"d":"न पश्यामि","m":"did not see"},{"d":"वानराः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"युद्धे","m":"in war"},{"d":"कदाचन","m":"even"},{"d":"जितपूर्वाः","m":"not failed to succeed"},{"d":"न चापि","m":"not seen."}]},{"v":18,"dev":"तदेतद्भयमुत्पन्नंत्रायस्वेमांमहबल ।नाशयत्वमिमानद्यतदर्थंबोधितोभवान्","trans":"\"Mighty strong I am, but such is the fear that has been created in me from them. You have been awakened, to destroy them. Reported Ravana.\"","words":[{"d":"महाबल","m":"mighty strong"},{"d":"तत्","m":"you"},{"d":"एतत्","m":"this"},{"d":"भयम्","m":"fear"},{"d":"उत्पन्नम्","m":"that is created"},{"d":"इह","m":"here"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"त्रायस्व","m":"from them"},{"d":"तम्","m":"you"},{"d":"अद्य","m":"rising"},{"d":"इमान्","m":"these"},{"d":"नाशय","m":"destroy"},{"d":"तदर्थम्","m":"by that"},{"d":"भवान्","m":"you"},{"d":"बोधितः","m":"reported."}]},{"v":19,"dev":"सर्वक्षपितकोशं च स त्वमभ्यवपद्यमाम् ।त्रायस्वेमांपुरींलङ्कांबालवृद्धावशेषिताम्","trans":"\" All resources of mine are exhausted. These children and aged are only left in Lanka city, knowing that you will save the city of Lanka.\"","words":[{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"सर्वक्षपितकोशम्","m":"all resources exhausted"},{"d":"माम्","m":"my me"},{"d":"अभ्यवपद्य","m":"striking at the enemy"},{"d":"बालवृद्धावशेषिताम्","m":"children and aged are only left"},{"d":"इमाम्","m":"these"},{"d":"लङ्कां","m":"Lanka"},{"d":"पुरीम्","m":"city"},{"d":"त्रायस्व","m":"by you."}]},{"v":20,"dev":"भ्रातुरर्थेमहाबाहो कुरुकर्मसुदुष्करम् ।मयैवंनोक्तपूर्वोहिकश्चिद्भ्रातः परन्तप","trans":"\"O broad shouldered brother! Do this task which is difficult for others. O Scourge of enemies! I have not asked you before for such a task.\"","words":[{"d":"महाबाहो","m":"broad shouldered"},{"d":"भ्रात","m":"brother:"},{"d":"परन्तप","m":"scourge"},{"d":"अर्थे","m":"you are"},{"d":"सुदुष्करम्","m":"difficult"},{"d":"कर्म","m":"task"},{"d":"कुरु","m":"do"},{"d":"भ्रातः","m":"brother"},{"d":"मया","m":"my"},{"d":"कश्चित्","m":"indeed"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"न उक्तपूर्वःहि","m":"not asked you before."}]},{"v":21,"dev":"त्वय्यस्तिममस्नेहःपरासम्भावना च मे ।दैवासुरेषुयुद्धेषुबहुशोराक्षसर्षभ त्वयादेवाःप्रतिव्यूह्यनिर्जिताश्चासुरायुधि ।","trans":"\"O Bull among Rakshasas! Being my brother, do this for me. I always have affection for you. Considering that you have encountered war with Devas and Asuras and won both Devas and Asuras, do this help.\"","words":[{"d":"राक्षसर्षभ","m":"bull among Rakshasas"},{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"त्वयि","m":"you"},{"d":"स्नेहः","m":"affection"},{"d":"अस्ति","m":"being"},{"d":"मे","m":"to me"},{"d":"परा","m":"others"},{"d":"सम्भावना च","m":"considering"},{"d":"दैवासुरेषु","m":"Devas and Asuras"},{"d":"युद्धेषु","m":"in war"},{"d":"प्रतिव्यूह्य","m":"encountered"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"by you"},{"d":"देवाः","m":"Devas"},{"d":"असुराः","m":"Asuras"},{"d":"युधि","m":"in war"},{"d":"बहुशः","m":"perhaps"},{"d":"निर्जिताः","m":"won."}]},{"v":22,"dev":"तदेतत्सर्वमातिष्ठवीर्यंभीमपराक्रम न हितेसर्वभूतेषुदृश्यतेसदृशोबली ।","trans":"\"O Brother of fierce valour! Get up. I have not seen anyone stronger than you among all beings.\"","words":[{"d":"भीमपराक्रमः","m":"of fierce valour"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"एतत्","m":"this"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"all"},{"d":"वीर्यम्","m":"heroism"},{"d":"आतिष्ठ","m":"get up"},{"d":"सर्वभूतेषु","m":"among all beings"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"बली","m":"stronger"},{"d":"न दृश्यतेहि","m":"not seen."}]},{"v":23,"dev":"कुरुष्वमेप्रियहितमेतदुत्तमंयथाप्रियंप्रियरणबान्धवप्रिय ।स्वतेजसाविधमसपत्नवाहिनींशरद्घनंपवनइवोद्यतोमहान्","trans":"\"You are a lover of wars. You are a lover of relations. You are always my dear well wisher. O self glorious one! Do this task of throwing out the torrent army just like wind throws rainy clouds.\" ।। इत्यार्षेवाल्मीकीयेश्रीमद्रामायणेआदिकाव्येयुद्धकाण्डेष्टितमस्सर्गः ।। This is the end of the sixty second sarga of Yuddha Kanda of the first epic the holy Ramayana composed by sage Valmiki.","words":[{"d":"प्रियरण","m":"lover of war"},{"d":"बान्धवप्रिय","m":"lover of relations"},{"d":"मे","m":"to me"},{"d":"प्रियहितम्","m":"well wisher"},{"d":"एतत्","m":"these"},{"d":"यथाप्रियम्","m":"always loving"},{"d":"कुरुष्व","m":"do this"},{"d":"स्वतेजसा","m":"self glorious"},{"d":"सपत्नवाहिनीम्","m":"torrent army"},{"d":"उद्यतः","m":"throws"},{"d":"महान्","m":"great"},{"d":"पवनः","m":"wind"},{"d":"शरद्घनम् इव","m":"rainy cloud"},{"d":"विधम","m":"in that way."}]}]}